! Morphological Transducer for aii

Multichar_Symbols

! Features
%[%-hab%] !  habitual - verb picks this tag up in LEXICON Prefixes
%[%+hab%] !  if verb picks this tag up later, will analyze with <hab>
%[%-fut%] !  future
%[%+fut%] !

! Part of speech categories
%<n%>   ! Noun
%<vblex%>   ! Verb (lexical)
%<adj%>   ! Adjective
%<prn%>   ! Pronoun
%<adv%>   ! Adverb
%<pr%>   ! Preposition

! Archiphonemes
%{A%}   ! > Alaf if word-final or word-initial, otherwise null

! Person morphology
%<p1%> ! First Person
%<p2%> ! Second Person
%<p3%> ! Third Person

! Gender morphology
%<m%> ! Masculine
%<f%> ! Feminine

! Number morphology
%<pl%>  ! Plural
%<sg%>  ! Singular

! Case morphology
%<nom%> ! Nominative
%<gen%> ! Genitive

! TAM morphology
%<hab%> ! Habitual
%<past%> ! Past
%<pres%> ! Pres
%<fut%> ! Future

! Pronoun morphology
%<obl%> ! Oblique

! Other symbols
%>      ! Morpheme boundary


